author: @Blah-Blah-Blah143
text: Winter describes this really well in that it sounds simple but really isn't. The beauty of the vocals in this song is the subtlety of tone delivery, intonation and accuracy in pronunciation on the delivery of each word on each beat. It really is a 'less is more' type of song.  Delivering simple words with colour isn't as easy as people think. If it was easy, it would just sound like monotone reading of lyric to a beat. Nice work AESPA.
